==Introduction==
''GAP was founded in 1989 to empower people to live and work increasingly sustainably.'' 
It is a network with member organizations in a score of countries. Programs have been developed for adults and children, including work places and schools. GAP International gives training in such topics as how to adapt a program for use in a different culture, how to design an empowering program, how to coach in an empowering way, how to lead a project (process) for [[sustainable development]]. http://www.globalactionplan.com

